{"tid":430891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英記者稱俄火箭運算能力不及iPhone　俄駐英大使館：可嘗試用iPhone上太空","createTime":"2017-10-10T08:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T15:47:22.000Z","uid":88681,"like":405,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ff2f93b323de79b437bd23599609a4b0bae6d9","tid":430891,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171009/s00005/020ca789feb92463b64a3fd04c4c9cbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171009%2Fs00005%2F020ca789feb92463b64a3fd04c4c9cbd.jpg&h=0e35cf53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一名記者在《星期日泰晤士報》撰文表示，俄羅斯聯盟號火箭的運算能力不及蘋果智能手機iPhone。俄羅斯駐英國大使館回應指，該記者可嘗試用iPhone飛上太空，不要乘搭「過時的」火箭。<br />\n<br />\n英國記者惠特爾（Gilles Whittell）於周日（8日）在《星期日泰晤士報》撰文表示，隨著蘇聯解體，俄羅斯航天技術沒有任何改善。雖然俄羅斯升級了聯盟號火箭的電腦系統，但系統運算能力仍然很小，甚至比不上一部iPhone。<br />\n俄羅斯駐英國大使館其後在社交網站twitter上表示，惠特爾或許能用iPhone飛上太空，而不是「過時的」聯盟號。<br />\n按照記錄，聯盟號火箭已發射超過1,500次，成功率達97％。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171009/s00005/1507537165886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171009%2Fs00005%2F1507537165886&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=257617b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171009%2Fs00005%2F1507537165886&h=d6769c47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171009/s00005/1507537165886</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俄佬都幾串"},{"pid":"afdce498e7977cf184d0c3dea31e7399e709a36a","tid":430891,"uid":69746,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"串過碼頭咕哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa